{#def 
    name,
    size="default",
    color=""
#}
{#-
Icon Component

Renders common SVG icons by name.
Names: chart, user, folder, blog, desktop, mobile, tablet, github, linkedin, email, phone, twitter, arrow-down, check, x, menu, search, plus, edit, trash, external-link
